
Ranger Help for: learn
======================

SYNTAX:      learn <skill name here>/learn cost for <skill name here>
USAGE:       Any wilderness terrain.

SUMMARY:    
Allows a Ranger to learn a skill from the slots list when the Ranger has
enough slots available. If you type 'learn cost <skill>', you will see the
slot cost, prerequisites, terrains, and unlocked skills.

============================================================================
SEE ALSO: slots, myinfo and myskills
